Definition: the act of turning your head left and right to signify denial or disbelief or bemusement
Example: I could tell from their headshakes that they didn't believe me
Synonyms: headshaking, motion, the, act, of, turning, your, head, left, and, right, to, signify, denial, or, disbelief, bemusement, I, could, tell, from, their, headshakes, that, they, didn, t, believe, me
Category: noun.act
